<p>Manoj M. Joshi and Robert M. Haberle (2012). Suppression of the water ice and snow albedo feedback on planets orbiting red dwarf stars and the subsequent widening of the habitable zone <span style="font-style:italic;">Astrobiology, 12</span> (1) DOI: <a href="http://dx.doi.org/http://arxiv.org/abs/1110.4525" rev="review">http://arxiv.org/abs/1110.4525</a></p>
