<article id="post-577" class="post-577 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-astronomy-and-exoplanets tag-astronomy tag-earth-masses tag-exoplanet tag-extra-solar-planet tag-gliese-667cc tag-habitable-zone tag-planetary-characteristics tag-red-dwarf tag-science tag-triple-star-system">
